# Homelab documentation (nerd.dad)

**All create/update work for homelab or cluster documentation goes in this repository.**

Published at: https://nerd.dad/latest/homelab/

| Content | Path |
|---------|------|
| Cluster guides (overview, nav, kubectl, Jellyfin history) | `docs/homelab/guides/` |
| Hand-written pages (`mk_*.md`) | `docs/homelab/` (mirrors cluster `kubernetes/` layout) |
| Shared runbook snippets | `includes/homelab/runbook/` |
| Site / blog (non-homelab) | `docs/` (blog, podcast, etc.) |

## Conventions

- Alert runbooks: `docs/homelab/kubernetes/my-apps/observability/runbooks/mk_runbook_*.md`
- Do **not** put runbooks under truecharts `clusters/` (breaks ClusterTool genconfig).
- HelmRelease YAML, PrometheusRules, and Flux manifests stay in **truecharts**.
- Alert annotations in truecharts should use:
  `https://nerd.dad/latest/homelab/kubernetes/.../mk_runbook_<slug>/`

There is no in-cluster MkDocs image — GitHub Pages is the docs host.
